      "id": 330188,
      "is_answer_order_important": false,
      "stimulus_html": "",
      "stem_html": "What about the second step in the electrophilic addition of HCl to an alkene—the reaction of chloride ion with the carbocation intermediate? Is this step exergonic or endergonic? Does the transition state for this second step resemble the reactant (carbocation) or product (alkyl chloride)? Make a rough drawing of what the transition-state structure might look like.",
      "answers": [],
      "hints": [],
